6. 📝 Additional Suggestions (Optional Features)
Google Drive synchronization

Dark mode support

Reminder notifications

Color-coded notes by priority or type

7. 🔚 Conclusion
This project delivers a fast, simple, and effective note-taking application that users can easily integrate into their daily lives. Developed with Flutter, it ensures compatibility and smooth performance across both Android and iOS platforms.
